<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدِيثُ ⦗٤٦٠⦘ الرَّبِيعِ بْنِ صُبَيْحٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣١٥٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> حَدَّثَنَا عَبَّاسٌ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ يَحْيَى يَقُولُ: الرَّبِيعُ بْنُ صُبَيْحٍ ثِقَةٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>